<div style="padding: 10px;">
        <p>We designed the project as a reflection on the current state where the Covid-19
pandemic has reminded us on how our life is under constant surveillance by
inhumane entities. Computers are storing the data of our lives while the owners of
our data and therefore our lives are unknown and leaving us to blindly accept their
terms and conditions. The main given functions of the website represent the three
ways of dealing with an imposed condition of something as simplistic as a queue
control. Be a passive observer and play the game of tracking others that is so often
being played on us. Be part of the market of interaction working with others to come
to a compromise by engaging oneself in a collective effort of trade. Or be a formalist
taking its issue with a higher representative - the institution that seems to be
responsible for your immediate problem. There remains and option of excluding
oneself from the game. Being presented with a notion of top - bottom organizational
scheme and choosing to ignore it. This category by itself is the most diverse. You can
range from a paranoiac to a denier. We are not only presenting the system to be
followed blindly but are throughout the process of collecting data most interested in
how one reacts to given options.</p>
